		<description><![CDATA[Apple will fill in coverage of its retail stores in the area south of Puget Sound (Wash.) when they locate a store inside the Tacoma Mall in that city. The mall is located along Interstate 5, and has just completed a 100,000 square-foot lifestyle expansion where Apple may locate. The Seattle region is now served [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Apple will fill in coverage of its retail stores in the area south of Puget Sound (Wash.) when they locate a store inside the <strong>Tacoma Mall</strong> in that city. The mall is located along Interstate 5, and has just completed a 100,000 square-foot lifestyle expansion where Apple may locate. The Seattle region is now served by four Apple stores, but they are all along the eastern rim of Puget Sound and at least 25 miles from Tacoma. The store could open by July 2009.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
