			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>A huge crowd packed the plaza in front of the new <strong>Rosenstrasse</strong> (Munich) retail store Saturday morning to await the moment when the door swung open for the first time. The weather was cold, but there was no rain or snow to dampen the spirits of the crowd. There were reportedly 4,000 visitors to the store within the first four hours.Â <strong>Dennis Voss</strong>, a veteran of several other grand openings in Europe and the United States, started the overnight waiting line at 1:30 a.m. and was first through the doors when the store opened at 10 a.m. Check photos of the waiting line and the grand opening on the setteB.IT <a title="Rosenstrasse grand opening" href="http://www.setteb.it/news-Folla-interminabile-per-l-Apple-Store-di-Monaco-2008-12-05-005308.xhtml">Web site</a>, these flickr sets by <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/smokeonit/sets/72157610821408068/">smokeonit</a> and <a title="Rosenstrasse opening by Oifi74" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/oifi/tags/store/">Oifi74</a> and <a title="Rosenstrasse Apple store" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/mki/tags/store/">Isik</a>, and this amazing panoramic <a title="Rosenstrasse grand opening panorama" href="http://homepage.mac.com/wkaemena/FS/Muenchen/AppleMUC1/" target="_blank">QTVR</a> of the storefront. Watch a YouTube video after the break, or surf this Vimeo <a title="Rosenstrasse video" href="http://vimeo.com/2447783">video</a>.<span id="more-3843"></span></p>
<div class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 660px"><img title="Rosenstrasse waiting line" src="http://www.ifoapplestore.com/photos/rosenstrasse_crowd.jpg" alt="The view of the crowd from the second level of the Rosenstrasse store" width="650" height="488" /><p class="wp-caption-text">The view of the crowd from the second level of the Rosenstrasse store</p></div>
<p>Watch this <a href="http://www.bitsundso.de/adventskalender/2008/12/07/apple-store-muenchen/">video</a> from the bitsundso.de Web site.</p>
